# Power digit sum - pseudocoding

1.Read an integer value from the user and store it in a variable n
2.Check IF n is greater than 0 and less than or equal to 16
   IF yes find the power of 2, raised to the power of the given input and store it in the pow variable 
   Conver pow to string and use FOR loop to add every digit of the power to get the sum
   print sum
3.ELSE print -1
